AUDIENCE: So they
can make money?

00:10:01.390 --> 00:10:01.920
BLADE KOTELLY:
Oh, to make money.

00:10:01.920 --> 00:10:02.560
Yes.

00:10:02.560 --> 00:10:03.420
To make money.

