01:09:30.880 --> 01:09:33.870
But everyone knows that
the heart beats like this.

01:09:33.870 --> 01:09:36.540
And everyone assumed
that the body

01:09:36.540 --> 01:09:40.380
needs that heart beat in order
for the biological processes

01:09:40.380 --> 01:09:42.149
to work as they're supposed to.

01:09:42.149 --> 01:09:43.939
Turns out, that's not the case.

01:09:43.939 --> 01:09:47.870
Turns out that if you pump
blood smoothly through the body,

01:09:47.870 --> 01:09:49.529
it works.

01:09:49.529 --> 01:09:52.670
You get oxygen from the lungs
to the parts that need it.

01:09:52.670 --> 01:09:55.830
And you actually can have a
working rotary heart pump.

01:09:55.830 --> 01:09:58.980
So Levatronix thought, well,
this would be a great thing

01:09:58.980 --> 01:10:02.930
to build except that the
spinning pump shaft has

01:10:02.930 --> 01:10:04.679
a bearing at either
end of the shaft

01:10:04.679 --> 01:10:06.970
and there's friction in the
bearing which creates heat,

01:10:06.970 --> 01:10:09.280
the heat creates
blood clots, the blood

01:10:09.280 --> 01:10:12.400
